# name|version|url|sha256|target_filename
# url supports:
#   - system://<cmd>        (copy from local PATH, offline-friendly)
#   - http(s)://...         (download + sha256 verify)
ffmpeg|system|system://ffmpeg|SKIP|ffmpeg
ffprobe|system|system://ffprobe|SKIP|ffprobe
mediainfo|system|system://mediainfo|SKIP|mediainfo
BDInfo|system|system://BDInfo|SKIP|BDInfo
